    <category term="Operating Systems" scheme="http://www.091209.xyz/tags/Operating-Systems/"/>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul class="wp-block-list">  <li>    能够访问Github  </li>  <li>    DiskGenius  </li>  <li>    BIOS支持64位UEFI（若不支持可参考下载链接中的教程）  </li></ul><p><strong>1.下载</strong><br>必须：<a href="https://github.com/M-L-P/grub2-fyde">Grub2 Fyde&nbsp;2</a></p><ul class="wp-block-list">  <li>    BIOS支持64位UEFI：<a href="https://github.com/M-L-P/Yours-UEFI">Yours UEFI 1</a>  </li>  <li>    不支持：<a href="https://github.com/M-L-P/Yours-LegacyBIOS">Yours LegacyBIOS</a>  </li></ul><p>（在此感谢上方Github仓库的贡献者！）<br>下载最新Release压缩包并解压</p><p><strong>2.安装EFI文件 （以下以支持64位UEFI为例）</strong><br>打开DiskGenius，选择SYSTEM_DRV分区并打开<br>按照以下步骤复制文件：</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">  <p>    注意：若想保留Windows原引导，忽略删除EFI\Boot步骤，并将压缩包中Boot中的Bootx64.efi更名为其他名称，否则Windows容易PIN码失效  </p></blockquote><p>Yours-UEFI:<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async"  src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image.png" /></figure> </p><p>Grub2-Fyde:  </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async"  src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-1.png" /></figure> </p><p><strong>3.调整引导顺序并安装证书</strong><br>在DiskGenius中转到&#8221;工具&#x3D;&gt;设置UEFI BIOS启动项&#8221;，按照图示新增&#x2F;修改原Windows引导项</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">  <p>    若不保留Windows原引导，请将启动文件替换为\EFI\Boot\Bootx64.efi  </p></blockquote><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/屏幕截图-2025-07-21-191433.png"  /></figure> </p><p>点击保存后，勾选“下次启动时…”，或将该启动项移至最前面，关闭电脑<br>在BIOS中暂时禁用安全启动（Secure Boot）<br>开机后，出现MokManager页面<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async"  src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-2.png" /></figure> </p><p>选择OK<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async"  src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-3.png"  /></figure> </p><p>按下任意键</p><p>选择Enroll key from disk<br>接下来找到ENROLL_THIS_KEY_IN_MOKMANAGER.cer，回车，选择Continue&#x3D;&gt;Yes&#x3D;&gt;Reboot<br>在BIOS中开启安全启动后，即可正常进入引导界面<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/image-4.png"  /></figure> </p><p>选择FydeOS，回车，之后即可在安全启动下正常使用FydeOS<br>之后的引导界面自定义可参考<a href="https://github.com/M-L-P/rEFInd-theme-Yours">rEFInd-theme-Yours&nbsp;</a></p>]]>
    </content>
